<F P=104>  London Kanal-6 Television </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Armenia is asking for Turkey's help in making peace 
with Azerbaijan. Zhirair Liparityan, deputy foreign minister of 
