<H3> <TI>   Pakistan Accuses India of `Atrocities' in Kashmir </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK1502161894 Islamabad PTV Television Network in English 
1400 GMT 15 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1502161894 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad PTV Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pakistan has called upon the United Nations Human 
Rights Commission to investigate the massive atrocities 
unleashed by Indian forces in occupied Jammu and Kashmir. 
Speaking at the Commission's current session in Geneva, 
Pakistani delegate Mr. Shafqat Kakakhel accused India of 
misusing the right of state to protect their territorial 
integrity for justifying brutal repression against the 
population of Jammu and Kashmir, whose final status has to be 
determined in accordance with the wishes of the people of Jammu 
and Kashmir. 

</TEXT>

