<DOCNO> FBIS3-39860 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drweu036_q_94005" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-WEU-94-036 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  23 Feb 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Meets With Foreign Minister </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2202151194 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1100 
GMT 22 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2202151194 </F>
