<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   PKK Attack Spills Nearly 700 Barrels in Batman </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2202220794 London Kanal-6 Television in Turkish 1700 GMT 
22 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2202220794 </F>
<F P=104>  London Kanal-6 Television </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The BOTAS [Pipeline and Petroleum Transport 
Corporation] oil terminal in Batman came under PKK [Workers 
Party of Kurdistan] rocket attack yesterday. The attack took 
place at 1910 last night. Three petrol tanks were hit in the 
attack, which was launched from the Mardin-Batman highway. 
Nearly 700 barrels of crude oil leaked from the tanks into the 
surrounding area but did not catch fire. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

