<H3> <TI>   Kliridhis Briefs EU Observer on Proximity Talks </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2202121894 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 1130 GMT 22 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2202121894 </F>
