<H3> <TI>   Papandreou Returns From Brussels, Comments </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2302201094 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in 
Greek 1800 GMT 23 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2302201094 </F>
