Language: <F P=105> Greek </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Greek Deputy Foreign Minister Yeoryios Papandreou 
said it is important that Skopje is again to the fore with our 
EU [European Union] partners. He said it is equally important 
that EU Commissioner Hans van den Broek is dealing with the 
overall issue of Skopje and not exclusively with the economic 
sanctions imposed by Greece against the neighboring statelet. 
Papandreou made his statement upon his return today from 
